12) Acceptance Checklists (Definition of Done)
	Per feature:

	Unit tests ≥90% critical paths.

	Integration tests cover success + 3 edge cases.

	Handles timeouts/errors gracefully.

	No leaks under Valgrind; clean ASan/UBSan.

	Throughput & latency not regressed vs previous tag.


13) Risks & Mitigations
	Parser ambiguity → Write EBNF first; golden tests for configs.

	CGI hangs → strict timeouts, signal handling, kill child group.

	Resource leaks → RAII wrappers; sanitizers mandatory in CI.

	Slowloris → header read timeout + per-conn header size cap.

	Path traversal → canonicalize to root; reject outside.